'''Al-Oruba Club Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Sakakah]], [[Saudi Arabia]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches, on club level by [[Al-Orobah F.C.]] of the [[Saudi Professional League]]. The stadium has a capacity of 8,000.

